lsm_boundary_conditions.h [code]lsm_boundary_conditions.h provides support for filling ghostcells to impose several common level set method boundary conditions in two- and three-dimensions. Support is provided for extrapolation and homogeneous Neumann boundary conditions. Boundary conditions are imposed by filling ghostcells outside of the computational domain in such a way that they produce the desired boundary condition
